org.usfirst.frc.team3494.robot.commands.auto

Class PathBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.usfirst.frc.team3494.robot.commands.auto.PathBuilder

  • public class PathBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for generating Pathfinder trajectories. All distances are in meters. All angles are in radians (conversion methods available with Pathfinder.d2r(double).)
